---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Results & Case Studies — SalesAtScale.io"
  description="Check out our most recent results, case studies, and clients. We've built and scaled high-ticket sales infrastructure for industry-leading companies."
>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-16 text-center">
    <h1 class="font-chivo font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[56px] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-6" style="color:#F8FAFC;">
      Check Out Some Of Our Most Recent <br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span class="text-blue">Results, Case Studies, & Clients</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-chivo font-medium text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto" style="color:#94A3B8;">
      We've built, managed, and scaled high-ticket sales infrastructure for industry-leading companies like <span class="font-bold" style="color:#F8FAFC;">EcomScale, Alpha Cap, Elite Masterminds, Scale Consulting,</span> & many more.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Case Studies Feed -->
  <main class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col gap-12 pb-24">

    <!-- Case Study #1 -->
    <a href="/case-studies/college-financial-aid-258-growth/" class="group block w-full rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 relative overflow-hidden no-underline" style="background:rgba(30,41,59,0.8); border:1px solid #334155;" onmouseenter="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,59,224,0.6)';this.style.boxShadow='0 20px 60px rgba(0,59,224,0.15)'" onmouseleave="this.style.borderColor='#334155';this.style.boxShadow='none'">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 relative z-10">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-[55%] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="w-fit mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full font-chivo font-bold text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors" style="border:1px solid #334155; color:#F8FAFC;">Case Study #1</div>
          <h2 class="font-chivo font-black text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6" style="color:#F8FAFC;">
            +$150k MRR Added in 90 Days Without The Founder Taking A Single Call
          </h2>
          <div class="font-chivo font-medium text-[17px] leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-4" style="color:#94A3B8;">
            <p>John at EcomScale always struggled with SDR churn and unpredictable lead follow-up. He was stuck taking closing calls himself just to maintain revenue.</p>
            <p>We stepped in, ripped out his leaky CRM, and placed <strong style="color:#F8FAFC;">3 fully-vetted, performance-driven reps</strong> into our custom infrastructure. Within 90 days, his close rate skyrocketed.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Time to Placement: <span class="font-bold">14 Days</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Close Rate Increase: <span class="font-bold">From 18% to 32%</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Founder Hours Saved: <span class="font-bold">25+ Hours/Week</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Revenue Added: <span class="font-bold text-blue">+$150,000 MRR</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="text-blue font-chivo font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Read Full Breakdown <span class="text-lg">&rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg aspect-video relative" style="border:1px solid #334155; background:#070A11;">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src="https://placehold.co/800x450/111827/475569?text=Slack+Win+Message" alt="Client Proof" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg relative" style="border:1px solid #334155; background:#070A11; aspect-ratio:21/9;">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/800x340/111827/475569?text=Stripe+Revenue+Dashboard" alt="Data Proof" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width="800" height="340" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Case Study #2 -->
    <a href="/case-studies/tax-strategy-10x-revenue/" class="group block w-full rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 relative overflow-hidden no-underline" style="background:rgba(30,41,59,0.8); border:1px solid #334155;" onmouseenter="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,59,224,0.6)';this.style.boxShadow='0 20px 60px rgba(0,59,224,0.15)'" onmouseleave="this.style.borderColor='#334155';this.style.boxShadow='none'">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 relative z-10">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-[55%] flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="w-fit mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full font-chivo font-bold text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors" style="border:1px solid #334155; color:#F8FAFC;">Case Study #2</div>
          <h2 class="font-chivo font-black text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6" style="color:#F8FAFC;">
            Doubled Close Rate & Reduced SDR Churn To Zero For High-Ticket Coaching Offer
          </h2>
          <div class="font-chivo font-medium text-[17px] leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-4" style="color:#94A3B8;">
            <p>Elite Masterminds had incredible lead flow from their paid ads, but their internal team couldn't convert them. They were cycling through cheap SDRs every 45 days.</p>
            <p>We built out a <strong style="color:#F8FAFC;">fractional VP of Sales infrastructure</strong>, implemented daily huddles, and re-engineered their script. Their close rate literally doubled overnight.</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Previous Close Rate: <span class="font-bold">12%</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>New Close Rate: <span class="font-bold text-blue">25% (Within 30 Days)</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>SDR Turnover: <span class="font-bold">Dropped to 0%</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 font-chivo font-medium text-[16px]" style="color:#F8FAFC;"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue"></div>Total Deal Volume: <span class="font-bold">$2.1M Pipeline Managed</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="text-blue font-chivo font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Read Full Breakdown <span class="text-lg">&rarr;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-[45%] flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg aspect-video relative" style="border:1px solid #334155; background:#070A11;">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <img src="https://placehold.co/800x450/111827/475569?text=LinkedIn+Profile+%2B+Post" alt="Client Proof" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg relative" style="border:1px solid #334155; background:#070A11; aspect-ratio:21/9;">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/800x340/111827/475569?text=CRM+Pipeline+Screenshot" alt="Data Proof" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" width="800" height="340" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Apply Banner -->
    <div class="w-full mt-8 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 text-center md:text-left" style="background:rgba(0,59,224,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(0,59,224,0.3);">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-chivo font-bold text-2xl mb-2" style="color:#F8FAFC;">Want to be our next case study?</h3>
        <p class="font-chivo font-medium" style="color:#94A3B8;">We strictly partner with established 7-figure businesses ready to scale.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/apply/" class="shrink-0 px-8 py-4 bg-blue hover:bg-blue-hover text-white font-chivo font-bold text-sm rounded-md shadow-btn-glow hover:shadow-btn-glow-hover transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 uppercase tracking-widest">
        See If You Qualify
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
